hgkDBE0iHT1RobwOOPMWA">Trung thu - 中秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BB%87u/Trung-thu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-nHlFqATwFxVjYcBjIAYviA">Trung thu nguyệt kỳ 2 - 中秋月其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BB%87u/author-yGOsh2Zg2gUgZ09A-P6xFA">Lý Kiệu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/T%E1%BB%B1-l%E1%BA%A1c-b%C3%ACnh-sinh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o/poem-whYucO7i_dnw-MljuGOXWA">Tự lạc bình sinh đạo - 自樂平生道</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-V%C4%83n-Tri%E1%BB%87u-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-chi-sanh-Th%C3%B4i-H%C3%A0m-t%C6%B0-nghi%E1%BB%87p-chi-t%C3%B4n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-chi-t%E1%BB%AD-tr%C3%B9ng-phi%E1%BA%BFm-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m/poem-W5jXMTl-3BcSWf7ZZNli0w">Vũ Văn Triệu thượng thư chi sanh, Thôi Hàm tư nghiệp chi tôn, thượng thư chi tử, trùng phiếm Trịnh giám tiền hồ - 宇文晁尚書之甥崔彧司業之孫尚書之子重泛鄭監前湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
